  And this is John\rquote s thing about, you know, \'93A nose for trou}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid14112971\charrsid14902524 ble\'94.  I got into the trouble!  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 
