d been to at that age, you had the deceased and his nearest and dearest, and perhaps a few friends, and the whole thing was a bit sad, but a funeral in Esh Winning was a community event.  This is when you could see community.  
And the first funeral I went to was somebody \endash  I think he\rquote d been in the Union \endash 
