.  It was really wonderful.  I mean, it nearly reduced me to tears.  I mean, it was an incredible experience.  You could really feel the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid9332008\charrsid14902524 
