s an on-line recruiting firm which started off as recruiting graduates for blue chip national and international compan
ies, but which now does general recruitment across the board.  Their great claim to fame was that they actually filled a vacancy in a big international corporation in one hour.  But he develops and maintains all the software, he manages, now, the team tha
t develops and maintains the software, but he does that from an office in his mother-in-law\rquote s house in South Tyrol.  I\rquote m very proud of them.  They\rquote ve both done good things.  I mean, I don\rquote 
t think I was a terribly good father.  I was nowhere near as good a father as my own father was.
