\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid3566045\charrsid14902524 Paul:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid7999863\charrsid14902524 
Yes.  I was thinking about theories and I meant to ask you, going back to Sparkbrook, the theory about housing classes, does that come from John Rex\rquote s earlier work, or was that developed during the study?
